ion available apply now user interface designer web  mobile if you love using technology and have great understanding of its users then heres your opportunity to work closely with project managers programmers designers and content writers to design some of the most awesome user interfaces for web and mobile applications of netccentrics main products such as nuffnang and churp churp read more job scope to come up with the concept and mockups for development in web and mobile to design user interfaces for netccentric inhouse development both for web and mobile to translate design mockups and wireframes into usable code templates both in web and mobile to be highly skilled and proficient in frontend coding languages html css responsive design javascript ios sdk andriod sdk to maintain the development of the product built both for web and mobile to create a solid user experience for each product thats being designed to come up with strong user task flow interaction models and screen designs and the details of the each element to optimize user experience to be able to develop products that have great balance between user experience and corporate direction requirements advanced skills in photoshop illustrator html  css  javascript ios sdk and android sdk great at typography design and art direction advanced knowledge of css good with scripting languages able to work with a team of programmers and other designers a kindred spirit full−time positions available apply now creative web designer htmlcss love seeing your designs all over the world wide web here you get to work closely with project managers programmers designers content writers and the sales team where youll be given the opportunity to design and maintain the corporate branding of the netccentric group − logos collaterals buntings banners websites for nuffnang churp churp and nom nom media read more job scope to code frontend development of nuffnang and churp churp in htmlcssjavascript to design and maintain corp